Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We beat Brain, and there's \Nonly one of Oracion Seis left!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were caught by a trap, \Nand Mr. Potato Head was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is also a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:17.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the light that's inside Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that, especially, is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:01.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the rumors say, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking you will totally \Nbe worth the effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop you and your idiotic goals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no stopping us! We are near!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Caitshelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, Titania...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:33.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, show me your true strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although your attacks still \Nwon't be able to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:48.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right. His magic, \NReflector, can bend away any attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way to defeat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:15.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Reflector will not be broken, \Nno matter how quickly you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two weaknesses to your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two{\i0} weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In just a short time, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness number 1:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to bend magic and objects,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but you are unable to bend human bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:02.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that were not the case, it would have \Nbeen faster to warp my body than my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, if I'm being \Nserious, I can finish you off with your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The second weakness: This!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said that attacks won't hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were bending my armor, \Nyou dodged my sword normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you bend the \Npath of the sword instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer: Because you can only bend \Nthings in one limited area at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The area around yourself, or \Nthe area around your enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must choose one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:26.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While you are casting your magic on me, you \Ncannot activate Reflector around yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible battle perception!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this, my Robe of Remoteness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is flexible armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic will not work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:50.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I guess if you include this \Narmor, that's three weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This fight is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will surrender without trouble now, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is already midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:14.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had let me finish you sooner, \Nyou could have slept peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have escaped facing the fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the bell that chimes midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:38.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it becomes midnight, my \Nwarping is taken to the extreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me for what's going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a Take Over... It's some \Nmagic power I've never felt before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rule was all a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no freedom in the Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:39.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the uprising,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared every night I couldn't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You all were also... in that tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what Cobra was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also your sin, Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:03.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You averted your eyes for eight years \Nfrom the suffering of your brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:10.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, at the end, you stand together with \NJellal, who should be the root of your hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the people who lost their lives \Nfor you, it is truly a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grampa Rob!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are their nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there... That's pretty cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You laid hands on your allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... That's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal, done in by your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait! Midnight's just begun \Nand there's still much more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him transform into a giant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My illusion didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:10:01.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did what I saw all happen while \Nthe bell was still ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but magic that affects \Nthe eyes doesn't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the most powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had surpassed my father... I was \Nthe strongest of the Six Generals...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you laugh at people's suffering, \Nthat goal will remain far out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:50.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to be able to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In a quiet place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This... is Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you never want to be defeated, you \Nmust first know your own weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:17.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And also... always be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:34.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him tumble, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think that's \Nthe main point here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:46.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great going, Natsu! Now, \Nbeat the crap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moving around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it down properly, you dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try dodging it instead, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle isn't pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again! The usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual over self-consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:12.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual "It's such trouble being so cute!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray! Lucy broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just a kid. Such a disappointment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! That guy's actually strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:41.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Is all you got your youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Youth alone isn't going to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You young'ns always showin' \Noff your young selves, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:50.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he might be a bit \Nself-conscious about his age...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:51.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on the mark, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think it's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:09.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All six... All Six Generals are wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:18.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is bad! Very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the eighth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's juicing like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about him, Jura beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain has another personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:09.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is the front face, codenamed \NBrain, who holds so much knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there is the back face, codenamed \NZero, who loves nothing but destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loves destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to his overwhelming, evil magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:29.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain sealed that existence \Naway himself with six keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And those are... Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the Six Generals fall, and \Ntheir Body Link magic is broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:46.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the personality of Zero will \Nbe reborn once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:03.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Master Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:12.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Klodoa, it seems things have \Ngotten quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even that Midnight was beaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I truly apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, it sure has been a \Nwhile, to have this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To have this body... This voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It all brings me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, Klodoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:53.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure made a mess out of my guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As its master, I will make you pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:05.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... the guildmaster of Oracion Seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:13.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground is shaking from his magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gettin' fired up, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt magic power this nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start by erasing this baldy \Nwho hurt this body's Brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:39.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna attack someone \Nwho can't even move?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My shield is being broken, just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:01.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he can move or not \Nisn't much of a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:05.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it has form, it's \Njust as fun to destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's... frozen stiff...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, Master Zero! \NExcellent work as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating these annoying \Nbrats like they were nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they still live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have form!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in too much of a hurry to stop Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That wound... And the fact you'd used \Nup nearly all your magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:54.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were barely even able to \Nstand, weren't you, Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:19:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. It doesn't change the fact \Nthat it was I who undid the seal on Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry and stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder for how long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:18.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will I be able to remain \Nanchored at this harbor known as battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:45.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, I'm at my limit. Let me rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for pushing you, Carla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:06.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. But this ancient city is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... No matter how \Nmuch we look, we won't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You getting weak-knees isn't going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Caitshelter will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide on one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want Jellal to stop this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you chase two rabbits at \Nonce, you won't catch either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We have to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we have to stop Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:48.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about other \Nthings, and keep searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:49.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop it! Right \Nnow, we have to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:09.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it! I can see it! \NI can see it, Master Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting! I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:16.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is it! I can see Caitshelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guild of the race that \Nhas sealed Nirvana for an eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have to do is destroy them, and \Nthen Nirvana can never be sealed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:32.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:38.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me, Klodoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Master Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction! All I want to do is destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be my first shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:05.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason. Until it no \Nlonger has a form left to destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:58.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, do you know about Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... It's the thing that Hibiki's \Nguildmark is a picture of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! It's supposed to be a winged horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just snakes, but \Nhorses with wings, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:11.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My character's being ripped \Noff right and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:13.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is having wings all the rage lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:16.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: From Pegasus to the Fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.91,0:24:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If wings are all the rage, \Nthen business will be booming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:24.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy... Are you some kind of merchandise?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:26.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
